article_title: Warm winter day brings coyotes out to play
article_text: Two coyotes were spotted roaming a semi-frozen Lake Calhoun in Minneapolis on Saturday. Although some onlookers were startled by their presence, it’s not uncommon for coyotes to wander the metro area. They are seen more frequently in the spring, however.
